Text: Nice upload, good quality. Anyone expecting something like Fall Out Boy will be disappointed - this is a big departure from the FOB sound. It sounds like an electropop-Motown album. I'm not a huge fan of the change, but I am a huge fan of Patrick - so I'll force myself to like it more.

Moderate quality.

Amazing songs, we all knew FOB was Patrick, he is the talent!

But remember He's not on a major label any more and if you want to continue to hear his orgasmic talent you'll have to go see him live and support him much more thoroughly.

EP = *****
